### Health
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Register
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organization_name": "Acme Lending",
  "name": "Admin User",
  "email": "admin@acme.test",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@acme.test",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Create contact
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/contacts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Borrower",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "phone": "+15555550100"
}

### Create invite with request items
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/invites
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contact_id": "{{contact_id}}",
  "title": "SBA Loan Package",
  "message": "Please upload the requested documents.",
  "due_at": "2026-07-01T17:00:00Z",
  "request_items": [
    { "title": "Tax Returns", "kind": "document", "required": true },
    { "title": "Bank Statements", "kind": "document", "required": true }
  ]
}

### Bulk create invites (one per contact) and send magic-link emails
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/invites/bulk_create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contact_ids": ["{{contact_id}}", "{{contact_id_2}}"],
  "title": "SBA Loan Package",
  "message": "Please upload the requested documents.",
  "due_at": "2026-07-01T17:00:00Z",
  "request_items": [
    { "title": "Tax Returns", "kind": "document", "required": true, "section_name": "Financials" },
    { "title": "Bank Statements", "kind": "document", "required": true, "section_name": "Financials" }
  ]
}

### Send invite
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/invites/{{invite_id}}/send_invite
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Client request magic link
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/client/magic-link
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "jane@example.com" }

### Client exchange magic token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/client/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{ "magic_token": "{{magic_token}}" }

### Client view invite by public token
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/client/invites/{{public_token}}
Authorization: Bearer {{client_token}}

### Client create presigned upload URL
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/client/request-items/{{request_item_id}}/upload-url
Authorization: Bearer {{client_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filename": "bank-statement.pdf",
  "content_type": "application/pdf"
}

### Client complete upload after PUT to S3/MinIO
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/client/request-items/{{request_item_id}}/complete-upload
Authorization: Bearer {{client_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storage_key": "{{storage_key}}",
  "filename": "bank-statement.pdf",
  "content_type": "application/pdf",
  "byte_size": 123456
}
